#offset Pyragard

1
{
  name { Upon the cliff top  }
  desc {
"   You are standing upon the top of a cliff over looking a rolling tundra.
Far to the north, rising above a dense, deep icy fog, you can see the tops
of a mountain range.  A small goat track leads north and down to the tundra
floor whilst the cliff top trail heads west.
  }
  sector { Hills }
  exits {
	to { n, 2 }
	to { w, Nodonn:0 }
  }
}

2
{
  name { A small goat track.  }
  desc {
"   You are standing in the middle of a goat track that leads to the tundra
floor below you and up to the top of a cliff.  Far to the north you can just
make out the tops of some mountains, but mostly they are obscured by a thick
icy fog that shrouds the northern end of the tundra valley.
  }
  sector { Hills }
  exits {
	to { s, 1 }
	to { d, 3 }
  }
}

3
{
  name { The Tundra  }
  desc {
"   You stand upon the tundra floor.  A freezing wind whips about you, ice
crystals stabbing at your face.  All around you, you see an endless sea of
rolling hills spreading off in all directions.  To the north the hills are
hazy and are lost in a frigid, cloudy fog.  To your south is a small goat 
track that leads up a tall cliff to it's top.
  }
  sector { arctic }
  flags { no_mob }
  exits {
	to { n, 4 }
	to { e, 6 }
	to { w, 5 }
	to { u, 2 }
  }
}

4
{
  name { The Tundra  }
  desc {
"   The vast wastes of the tundra cover you on all sides you begin to feel that
your own mortality, for this is a timeless place. Where someone could starve to
death easily.  Just to the north the freezing fog obscures your view of the
mountains you know lurk beyond them.
  }
  sector { arctic }
  exits {
	to { n, 15 }
	to { e, 9 }
	to { s, 3 }
	to { w, 8 }
  }
}

5
